	* test/test4.c:
	- Updated test. 4 application switcher working at the same time.
	* libhildonwm/hd-entry-info.c:
	- Check if we have that entry for an specific application.
	* libhildondesktop/hn-app-switcher.c:
	- Code cleanup.

