	* libhildonwm/hd-keys.c: Fixed shortcuts to active tn/ap buttons.
	* libhildonwm/hd-wm.[ch]: 
	- Added method to have a reference of others menu.
	- Now hd-wm is able to focus any gtkwindow (and subclasses).

